Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, I didn't give anyone the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I protected Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll get you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's touching to see you two together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Soul Sealing Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking after Mokuba boy's soul for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want Mokuba boy back,\Nyou'll have to defeat me in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I challenge you right now!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight me right now.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you must fight with Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only face me\Nif you defeat Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Destined Battle!\N Yugi VS Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot defeat Yugi boy,\Nyou will never get a chance to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, Mokuba boy's soul\Nwill never be released from this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus... you bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be aware of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the ends of this tie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tightly pulling against each other, sharing the same fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bound together in a fate of fighting one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come for two Duelists\Nto intersect once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must bet those Star Chips in your fight with Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, Kaiba Corporation's reputation\Nwill surely be returned to what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am positive they {\i1}eagerly{\i0} await your return...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus... right now I have no choice but to do what you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but while I have no clue \Nhow you've done this trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens to Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you forget that "tie of fate"\Nis wrapped around {\i1}your{\i0} neck too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're out of that cave at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on the island are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Pegasus' castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it here, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, you appear so gentle right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I watch you in a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you have a look on your face that's almost scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's one Yugi who's gentle and sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that scary looking Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as if there really were \Ntwo separate Yugis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was my first time seeing \Nboth Yugis at the same time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's two Yugis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really didn't get it, but to put it simply, there's a cool Yugi and a normal Yugi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! I'll show you that I can be cool too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll defeat the hidden enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was that all just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Must have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you slow us down we're gonna\Ngo on without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be pointless for us to enter\NPegasus' castle by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Owww~\N -Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you were more reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two customers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are these two guys here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's against school rules to\Nhave a part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in big trouble now that\Nthat big mouth Jounouchi has seen me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she's been working \Nat Burger World, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright! I know her secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Knock it off! Anzu's getting mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enjoy our special hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please have {\b0}lots{\b1} of our popular ketchup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell and you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-why are you doing this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, you already found out,\Nso there's no need to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm saving money so I can go\Nto America after I graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}America?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Umm....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To study dance in New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would we laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing! That's amazing! We'll support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"After school, meet me in the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't come,\NI'll tell everyone your secret"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi! Or Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know what you guys are planning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll be expelled if your school\N finds out you've been working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you'd better keep your mouth\Nshut and do what I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think I'll just keep\Nquiet about it later!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're in no position to be making threats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you do to Anzu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}OWW!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want to play this sick game,\Nplay with {\b0}me{\b1} instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you say to having \Na little game with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}Game{\b1}, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We both draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The loser is the one with the weakest card.\NA one draw match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the loser will be \Nsent to the Dark World.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got this powerful card, \NCurse Of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a ridiculous game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see how you win a {\b0}man's{\b1} fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mind Crush!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A demon was running around here while you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my life in the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, that guy\Nwas already knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, it's kind of crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like there's two separate Yugis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cool but scary Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a gentle, but not so reliable Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, sometimes I feel like\NI have another me inside myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Yugi is Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OI! YUGI! ANZU!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, as I thought you've earned 10 Star Chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaiba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand my fate on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you live,\Nyou'll always be a thorn in my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winds of battle blow when we fight\Nlike a powerful tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun, stop starting trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! I'll be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll punch your lights out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU BASTARD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He showed you up the last time you fought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun, that went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this loser dog {\i1}also{\i0} collected 10 Star Chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I promote you from "loser dog" to "nobody"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sunova...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was searching for an answer after my last match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why did I lose to Yugi in that Duel?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How did Yugi summon a miracle at that time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I finally found an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Yugi possessed \Nsomething I didn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is a person stronger when they shoulder\Nthe weight of protecting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only way to find out is to defeat\Nyou in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, if you want to enter the castle,\Nyou have to defeat me {\i1}first{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Duel of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Kaiba-kun standing before me is different\Nthan the Kaiba-kun in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something is hidden in those eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun! You can't accept this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already collected \N10 Star Chips, it's pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Duelist blood has brought us together\Nonce again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duelist... blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will {\i1}defeat{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me to the stage of our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 Star Chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I permit you to enter\NPegasus' castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm the first one\Nto enter Pegasus' castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, we'll each bet 5 \NStar Chips on this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the one who wins may\Nenter Pegasus' castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use Duel Disks for this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuffle your cards and place your\Ndeck in the Deck Holder on your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Points 2000!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter set!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, don't you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick that Kaiba bastard's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I wonder who my opponents are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll enjoy this match from the\Ncastle's balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got out of the cave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The runner of Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be an interesting show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me.\NA great way to kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Yugi!\NIt's time to determine the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use these Duel Disks to have the\Nultimate card battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept any Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaiba, I {\i1}will{\i0} defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gargoyle Powered in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that when I fought him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse Of Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, though we are enemies now,\Nwe both share the same objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To beat Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. But if you really want to\Nsee him defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, your only option is to lose to me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's impossible for you to beat Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus' card strategy is to read people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not sure if it's some psychic power,\Nor a trick of some kind, but it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this card battle, I can use the Solid Vision
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to hide my body and face, and keep out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus' power is useless in front of the Duel Disks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba doesn't realize Pegasus' power comes\Nfrom the power of the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think the Duel Disk system will\Nhave an effect on a Dark Game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get my Gargoyle Powered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! All there is to do is attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Curse Of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Gargoyle Powered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Gargoyle Powered is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you came at me with no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth taking the first hit and losing Life Points to make sure you're taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Don't be scared of Kaiba's bluff, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. I'll draw a new card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Swordstalker The Avenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordstalker the Avenger channels the anger of his fallen comrades into his sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increases his Attack Points up by 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Revenge actually makes his Attack Points {\i1\b1}stronger{\i0\b0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that why he let me destroy\NGargoyle Powered so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now my monster's Attack Points are\N{\b0}greater{\b1} than Yugi's Curse Of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Swordstalker The Avenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Curse Of Dragon disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I have the \NMonster Replace card here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic Card switches a Monster targeted on my board
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and switches it with a Monster in my Hand with higher Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monster Replace...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster in my hand with \Nthe highest Attack is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician beat \NSwordstalker The Avenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, don't you underestimate Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, fighting you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes my heart beat faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I replay Curse Of Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La Jinn, The Genie Of The Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician, attack La Jinn, \NThe Genie Of The Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lamp deflects your attack\Nat your {\i1}own{\i0} Monster!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(323,455,14,455,2000,2500)}Curse Of Dragon is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! To trap {\i1}me{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I applaud you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, the {\i1\b1}real{\i0\b0} trap I've set for you\Nis just {\i1\b1}beginning{\i0\b0}..!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heart of the world's {\i1\b1}strongest{\i0\b0} Monster\Nhas already begun to beat in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to {\i1\b1}fuse{\i0\b0} 3 Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(131,144)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun and Yugi continue their Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! \NWe don't know what Kaiba-kun is planning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck Destruction Virus of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of Yugi's Monsters with more than\N1500 Attack Points are destroyed! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the fusion of 3 Blue-Eyes\NWhite Dragons been completed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: {\c&HFFFFFF&}"The Strongest! The Magnificent!\NBlue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
